abstract: 
  With the rise of accessible LLMs, the recent area of study has been 
  machine-generated tweets and their influence on various aspects. 
  This research aims to provide novel machine- generated misinformation 
  datasets and evaluate detectors for classifying 
  machine-generated misinformation tweets.

